extensions.description: AIpeCoin is the ultimate meme coin on Solana, blending the fun of meme culture with the revolutionary potential of AI technology. Designed for community engagement, airdrops, and decentralized trading, AIpeCoin aims to lead the next wave of blockchain-based innovation.
extensions.creator: L
roadmap: Phase 1: Launch token and initial community building
Phase 2: Establish liquidity pools on Raydium and Serum
Phase 3: Partner with AI projects for meme-driven AI dApps
Phase 4: Expand adoption through gamified experiences

tokenomics.burnMechanism: 2% of every transaction fee is burned to reduce supply over time.
